messages.content: This General Election is a clear choice between Labour that works for working people - or the Tories who support the privileged few. I've seen how hard life has been for people because of the Tory-led Coalition. Our town deserves better! I'm standing to serve the local community and people in Northampton. I have been appalled at the way this Tory-led government has hurt so many people here.

contactInformation.address: Reeble 9th at a Stithy Street, Northampton, NN2 6JG
